name: Mewtwo V-UNION Special Collection
extCardText:
Introducing Pokémon V-UNION: a single powerful Pokémon divided into four cards! When you rise to the challenge and put it all together (with the help of Professor Burnet), each fantastic Pokémon V-UNION brings four amazing attacks into battle at your side. Find more treasures in Pokémon TCG booster packs, and prepare to unleash a Pokémon V-UNION!

Each Pokémon TCG: Mewtwo V-UNION Special Collection includes:
• 4 promo cards that make up a single Pokémon V-UNION for Mewtwo V-UNION!

• 4 Pokémon TCG booster packs
